messages.message: This is a weird string. I assume it's `Start processing your <PROJECT_NAME> application!`, which makes sense only if your documents are, in fact, applications. We could just change this to `Start processing your documents.`
thanks! just put up a PR for this: https://github.com/instabase/instabase/pull/53194

LOL, it just struck me that this was referring to application as in your IDP app, not application as in your mortgage application. 'Sok, I still stand by the recommendation, because what even is an app? :joy:
